{"tid":943293,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《斷背山》成美國國寶 李安：原本只是想講愛情故事","createTime":"2018-12-16T12:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T01:33:49.000Z","uid":41343,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aebfd6b3bf68fcf714ce4f66776e53f16099c4e7","tid":943293,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"美國國會圖書館（Library of Congress）今年新增25部收藏電影，作為國寶流傳後世。台灣名導李安執導的《斷背山》名列其中，李安得知後表示，當初創作《斷背山》最大目的不是要用來反映社會現象，只是想講一個愛情故事，「令我驚訝的是，這部電影竟與觀眾有這麼深刻的共鳴。」<br />\n<br />\n李安在聲明上表示：「這部電影成為了文化的一部分，反映了暴力、偏見與愛的黑暗和光明。」《斷背山》當年獲奧斯卡金像獎8項提名，最後抱回最佳導演、最佳改編劇本及最佳電影配樂等3獎。另外史蒂芬史匹柏（Steven Spielberg）執導的《侏羅紀公園》、經典恐怖片《鬼店》、希區考克（Alfred Hitchcock）的《蝴蝶夢》以及奧黛麗赫本（Audrey Hepburn）主演的經典《窈窕淑女》。迪士尼1950年的《仙履奇緣》是今年唯一一部動畫。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會圖書館自1989年起每年都會挑選多部電影收藏，入選影片不限長短、是否曾公映，唯一要求是影片必須完成超過10年，旨在保護美國歷史和文化影像。今年恰逢國會圖書館30周年，館長卡拉海登（Carla Hayden）說：「在過去成千上萬部電影中，我們看到了自己，我們的多樣性、創造力、習慣和文化，我們的成功或失敗。這是值得保存的遺產。」"},{"pid":"756b4dae250a2518f99a58b81814c540c9837189","tid":943293,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46c3e8a661de5e204ee1cf8fe819640e158b7b5","tid":943293,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"有冇full list?"},{"pid":"f6044968026b3ec2d2edf9a0aa79a1474b63d9f2","tid":943293,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"中國的圖書館有無話收藏咩戲?"},{"pid":"757202337c1df7fb30af9ffb84d5c86e931d5efa","tid":943293,"uid":37586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f6044968026b3ec2d2edf9a0aa79a1474b63d9f2","tid":943293,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"中國的圖書館有無話收藏咩戲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"戰狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8016ecd2fb3744b4c78d9c5528f2ff5c1dced0","tid":943293,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"記者昨天從中國國家博物館藝術開發中心獲悉，國博將永​​久收藏電影《猛龍》。這是中國電影誕生百年之際唯一被國博列為館藏藝術品的影片，也是國家博物館有史以來首次將一部電影列為館藏品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2005-10-19/06497208380s.shtml?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2005-10-19%2F06497208380s.shtml%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3dcc8fe0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2005-10-19/06497208380s.shtml?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2005年10月19日"},{"pid":"7395b5cef30105abc8c23c5267b71869df2cda95","tid":943293,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f8016ecd2fb3744b4c78d9c5528f2ff5c1dced0","tid":943293,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"記者昨天從中國國家博物館藝術開發中心獲悉，國博將永​​久收藏電影《猛龍》。這是中國電影誕生百年之際唯一被國博列為館藏藝術品的影片，也是國家博物館有史以來首次將一部電影列為館藏品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2005-10-19/06497208380s.shtml?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2005-10-19%2F06497208380s.shtml%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=oNcq5Rmqc0LEDkjZ1mequmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3dcc8fe0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2005-10-19/06497208380s.shtml?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2005年10月19日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"笑死人"},{"pid":"2a0e65065f5fd20461290aa482f9684b91c0282a","tid":943293,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6044968026b3ec2d2edf9a0aa79a1474b63d9f2","tid":943293,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"中國的圖書館有無話收藏咩戲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"抗日神劇"},{"pid":"9fedc4356d32e62a0a052d3cf3891005776ae92d","tid":943293,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6044968026b3ec2d2ed